#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/validate-decimals.md:1
msgid "_validate_decimals"
msgstr "_validate_decimals"

#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/validate-decimals.md:3
msgid "Firma"
msgstr "Signature"

#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/validate-decimals.md:9
msgid "Che problema risolve"
msgstr "What problem it solves"

#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/validate-decimals.md:11
msgid ""
"Verifica che la precisione usata per etichette e legende resti leggibile "
"e coerente tra le funzioni di plotting del package."
msgstr "Ensures that the precision used for labels and legends remains readable and consistent across the package plotting functions."

#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/validate-decimals.md:13
msgid "Contratto sugli input"
msgstr "Input contract"

#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/validate-decimals.md:15
msgid "`decimals` deve essere un intero vero oppure uno `np.integer`."
msgstr "`decimals` must be a real integer or an `np.integer`."

#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/validate-decimals.md:16
msgid "I booleani vengono rifiutati esplicitamente."
msgstr "Booleans are explicitly rejected."

#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/validate-decimals.md:17
msgid "Il valore deve essere compreso tra 0 e 20."
msgstr "The value must be between 0 and 20."

#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/validate-decimals.md:19
msgid "Dove viene usata"
msgstr "Where it is used"

#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/validate-decimals.md:21
msgid ""
"in [`histogram`](../../moduli/plot_utils/histogram.md) per formattare "
"tick, media e banda"
msgstr "in [`histogram`](../../moduli/plot_utils/histogram.md) to format ticks, the mean, and the band"

#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/validate-decimals.md:22
msgid ""
"in [`lin_fit`](../../moduli/fit_utils/lin-fit.md) per formattare la "
"legenda del fit quando serve"
msgstr "in [`lin_fit`](../../moduli/fit_utils/lin-fit.md) to format the fit legend when needed"

#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/validate-decimals.md:24
msgid "Come fallisce"
msgstr "How it fails"

#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/validate-decimals.md:26
msgid "`ValueError` se `decimals` non e un intero"
msgstr "`ValueError` if `decimals` is not an integer"

#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/validate-decimals.md:27
msgid "`ValueError` se `decimals < 0`"
msgstr "`ValueError` if `decimals < 0`"

#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/validate-decimals.md:28
msgid "`ValueError` se `decimals > 20`"
msgstr "`ValueError` if `decimals > 20`"

#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/validate-decimals.md:30
msgid "Perche resta privata"
msgstr "Why it remains private"

#: ../../source/checks/plot_utils/validate-decimals.md:32
msgid ""
"E una regola di validazione orientata alla presentazione, condivisa "
"internamente dalle API di plotting ma non pensata come utilita pubblica "
"autonoma."
msgstr "It is a presentation-oriented validation rule, shared internally by the plotting APIs but not intended as a standalone public utility."

